---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="参与贡献" description="帮助完善TicNav抽动症信息导航站">
  <h1 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">参与贡献</h1>
  <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">TicNav 是一个由患者和家属共同维护的信息站，你的每一条建议都可能帮到其他家庭</p>

  <section class="mb-6">
    <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">你可以贡献什么</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
      <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white">
        <div class="text-xl mb-1">🏥</div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900">推荐医院 / 医生</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">你去过的抽动症专科门诊，靠谱的医生名字和所在医院</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white">
        <div class="text-xl mb-1">📋</div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900">指南 / 文章链接</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">权威机构发布的诊疗指南、专家科普文章链接</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white">
        <div class="text-xl mb-1">💬</div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900">病友社区 / 群</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">活跃的病友群、公众号、论坛，方便大家找到同伴</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white">
        <div class="text-xl mb-1">🔧</div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900">纠错 / 改进建议</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">发现信息有误、链接失效、或有更好的表达方式</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-6">
    <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">怎么提交</h2>
    <div class="space-y-3">

      <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border-2 border-indigo-200 bg-indigo-50">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
          <span class="text-lg">📧</span>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-indigo-900">发邮件（最简单）</h3>
          <span class="text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-indigo-600 text-white">推荐</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-600 mb-2">把你想补充的内容发到下面的邮箱，说明类型（医院/指南/社区/纠错）即可，我们会在3个工作日内录入。</p>
        <a href="mailto:425800970@qq.com" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm font-semibold text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
          425800970@qq.com
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
          <span class="text-lg">🐙</span>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900">GitHub Issue（适合技术用户）</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-600 mb-2">在仓库提交 Issue，审核后合并录入。</p>
        <a href="https://github.com/ticnav-cn/ticnav/issues/new" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-xs text-indigo-600 hover:underline">
          github.com/ticnav-cn/ticnav →
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 text-xs text-gray-500">
    <p>所有贡献在录入前会经过人工审核，确保信息可追溯、链接可访问。药品信息不包含剂量建议，病友经验类内容会添加提示说明。</p>
  </section>
</Base>
